data.description: Check your Natwest bank accounts from Perl
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This module will provide a perl interface onto the Natwest online
    banking system.

    The related modules Finance::Bank::HSBC, Finance::Bank::Barclays,
    and Finance::Bank::Lloyds all provide similar functionality for
    other banks, but there is no module for Natwest yet.
